15:36:49.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入嚟幫手推下<br />\n<br />\n白宮支持香港獨立聯署-光復香港唔係得把口<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1950151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1950151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"58fbe79e39f956f7ea0a52c299455e6ca7a5e541","tid":1950653,"uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T15:39:55.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺做左防疫專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27aba51c61433f92f37ca70ab3de350e898aeacf","tid":1950653,"uid":53510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T15:44:48.000Z","msg":"聽撚左幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c73fb602c682b86a4fecc896917fd1609d24b1","tid":1950653,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"又老實講 守住每一日都真係好緊要<br />\n武漢肺炎個疫情真係無了期<br />\n危機感永續14先可以笑到最後"},{"pid":"2fdcb9f009ca5a0c7c0de66b5194f6a1f30076c1","tid":1950653,"uid":260852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5277e3b49137d0e723e19b9e652f652a01973878","tid":1950653,"uid":46151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H0Wp3fP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH0Wp3fP.jpg&h=6f7d6393&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T15:46:06.000Z","msg":"呀...4月都來緊啦"},{"pid":"33b3f9b235238e8780eda619184fcc83c9062675","tid":1950653,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T15:46:37.000Z","msg":"挑戰雲加48小時"},{"pid":"520a13cd56ccd27126394ef591433c5ef9fe8eb3","tid":1950653,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T15:48:27.000Z","msg":"永續未來14日"},{"pid":"530d021aa4821f9c1c82384439060623a20c5f1b","tid":1950653,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d4f96706ef2703b228bb85606d5cbc4bac71da7","tid":1950653,"uid":57397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T12:41:33.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】大家都想問疫情何時受控？專家說，4月1日前個案沒有急升，可以說先過了一關，代表3月19日前沒有接受檢疫的人沒有引發社區大爆發，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但未來兩星期仍然是關鍵。</span></strong><br />\n短短一個月多了590宗確診，超過七成與外地輸入有關，再看近三天個案，九成是19日，即實施強制檢疫後發病。專家指這些都是預計之內，若未來兩日沒大規模爆發，可以說先過了一關。<br />\n中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌表示：「去到四月一日，19日前回港、不需作家居檢疫的人士如果要發病已經發病了，當然他們亦將病毒帶入社區，去到四月中，如果數字沒再上升，開始回落，代表疫情開始受控；但相反如果社區繼續出現不明來歷、找不到源頭的群組，便令人擔心。」他說現時不明源頭約有六個群組。<br />\n另一專家袁國勇指，近期如酒吧爆發，都是與大家鬆懈，未有做好追蹤有關。袁國勇表示：「現時開始有少少進入失控狀態，香港測試數目很低，於是在社區輕微病症根本沒有測試到，以致我們沒法很快切斷傳播鏈，即使診斷病症，追蹤也做得很慢，不夠時間做。如果我們再做不好，我們變了意大利北部般。」<br />\n最近三日，百多宗確診個案中已經有30多個病人沒病徵，專家說要保持社交距離以及個人衞生，才可以防止隱形傳播。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/21806\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F21806&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2ZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=d7e746a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F21806&h=7d426b2b\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/21806</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T15:50:56.000Z","msg":"K11 有店員確診。28號先開始無返工。<br />\n大家唔好再周圍走。"},{"pid":"ba8cc72f4962fcd6255dd43e2b5adcb097d9a471","tid":1950653,"uid":96909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T16:00:23.000Z","msg":"食屎啦專家"},{"pid":"f3ff143ad7786099e59789b12381e8b7c1394410","tid":1950653,"uid":52596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T16:04:50.000Z","msg":"每日都係未來的十四日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27901ef1f098cb56e495aff24b26c54c862b579c","tid":1950653,"uid":12432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T16:16:54.000Z","msg":"同阿仙奴轉會最後48小時一樣"},{"pid":"10a2e18b45f7ef5aafc216c59a6b09cba5f2421c","tid":1950653,"uid":20750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T16:24:12